    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070320/extras/ae63923066712ff90738227e779c7371.poster.avif?t=1563252844\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070320/extras/ae63923066712ff90738227e779c7371.webm?t=1563252844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070320/extras/ae63923066712ff90738227e779c7371.mp4?t=1563252844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>故事讲述一个不知名的小镇克拉那，一座凭空出现的洞穴吸引着冒险者的光临。地牢中盛产的指环，能给佩戴者带来强大魔力，使其可以控制元素和驾驭生物的力量。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070320/extras/b8a104df90e8f0f16a5357b853ff9185.avif?t=1563252844\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><br>随行的宠物，涌入的动物，洞穴中的穴居生物，地下怪异生物也捡起指环，获得强大的力量和智慧，阻碍和屠戮着冒险者。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070320/extras/eaa1e55a93c90ead08563dd8d2c47a11.avif?t=1563252844\" width=600 height=423 /></span><br><br>人类的贪婪致使他们不断向下挖掘。真相又是什么呢？底层又有什么等待着我们呢？<br><br><br><br>游戏中大量充斥着“指环使用者”间的战斗：<br>“指环使用者”之间的战斗会由这样“手手相觑”的方式表达，玩家确认了行动后，怪物会同时进行行动。互相猜测和反制是战斗的核心。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070320/extras/6de01d0f17bdb1f64b575637fd884020.poster.avif?t=1563252844\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070320/extras/6de01d0f17bdb1f64b575637fd884020.webm?t=1563252844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070320/extras/6de01d0f17bdb1f64b575637fd884020.mp4?t=1563252844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>